            <title>[LU-9813] Luster filesystem failover problem from one OSS server to another.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9813</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have two OSS Servers ( HP DL 360 G). One of the OSS server was failed. As per configuration Lustre file system should be fail over to another server but it didn&apos;t happen.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are manually trying to failover  the filesystem but it is not working.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Please someone give us solution. As it is very urgent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
